patthana9.14:1.1_0: Nokilesaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanokilesaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana9.14:2.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.14:5.1_0: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… āsevane ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana9.14:7.1_0: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana9.14:8.1_1: naasaṅkilesikañceva nano ca kilesaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca ….
patthana9.14:9.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.14:10.1_1: naasaṅkiliṭṭhañceva nano ca kilesaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe…
patthana9.14:10.1_3: nakilesavippayuttañceva nano ca kilesaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe….
